name: An Unusual Amount Of Fear (V)
Lore: 'The peacekeepers of the galaxy are not to be taken lightly.',
Text: 'Deploy on Jedi Council Chamber or Yoda''s Hut.  Once per turn, may use 1 Force to take a card with ''A Jedi''s'' in title (except A Jedi''s Resilience) into hand from Reserve Deck; reshuffle.  [Virtual Block 5] Wipe Them Out, All Of Them and opponent''s [Sidious] Effects here are canceled. (Immune to Alter.)',
